imdb.plot outline: Rich NY Developer is offering to give away 4 multimillion dollar units in his new building to the most qualified and prestigious college graduates. Four drunk friends living in IOWA decide to make fake credentials and win those 4 units and move to NY. Once they get to NY they didn't realize how famous they now are, and now everyone wants to hire them in their expert field, but they don't have any clue what they are doing.
imdb.title: Lamb for Slaughter
plot: Rich NY Developer is offering to give away 4 multimillion dollar units in his new building to the most qualified and prestigious college graduates but four drunk friends living in Iowa decide to make fake credentials and win those 4 units.::Max Bobritsky
